---
---

<article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl bg-slate-950 text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-950 border border-slate-200 dark:border-transparent shadow-lg my-8 relative overflow-hidden transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-600/10 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <h4 class="font-display font-extrabold text-lg">Inscreva-se na nossa newsletter técnica</h4>
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-300 dark:text-slate-600 mt-1">Fique por dentro das novidades técnicas semanais de design e desenvolvimento diretamente no seu e-mail.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Simple inline form -->
    <form 
      id="newsletter-form" 
      toolname="assinarNewsletterTecnica"
      tooldescription="Assina a newsletter técnica de design e desenvolvimento do Doug Design com o endereço de e-mail."
      toolautosubmit="true"
      class="flex items-center gap-2 max-w-sm shrink-0 w-full md:w-auto" 
      onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); document.getElementById('newsletter-form').classList.add('hidden'); document.getElementById('newsletter-success').classList.remove('hidden');"
    >
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Seu e-mail" required class="bg-white/10 dark:bg-slate-100 border border-zinc-700/60 dark:border-slate-300 rounded px-3 py-2 text-xs placeholder-zinc-500 dark:placeholder-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-500 flex-grow md:w-48 text-white dark:text-slate-900" />
      <button type="submit" class="bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider px-4 py-2 rounded">Enviar</button>
    </form>
    <div id="newsletter-success" class="hidden text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400 flex items-center gap-1.5 py-2">
      <span class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/15 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[10px]">✓</span> Inscrito com sucesso! Obrigado.
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
